long_description: mid contracting company ltd. is a jordan-based construction contractor established in 1991 as a limited liability company. the founders modestly started the company targeting the local market, with an eye on the regional and international markets. over the last 30 years, the unremitting dedication and hard work of its distinguished professional team coupled with the willpower and determination of its founders, have granted mid contracting the aptitude to construct several specialized projects in jordan and abroad. in the year 1997, mid contracting was the first jordanian general contracting company to achieve the iso 9002 certification. in 2008, mid contracting moved under mid global investment group (mgig) which was originally established by the same founders in 2002 as private shareholding company. this corporate restructuring intended to integrate and complement the capacity of the group and its flagship, mid contracting, towards approaching a range of bot, boot, and dbot projects, as well as ppp projects.
